Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:29.67,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is there no final{\i}\N{\i1}piece to unravel this puzzle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:36.97,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wander around the search area with dread{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:44.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With shaky self-confidence{\i}\N{\i1}facing unyielding damnation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:48.31,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still alive, but I can't catch up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:54.53,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to residual images of hidden memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:58.74,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let loose dark shame unbounded{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the ends of this world of kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:06.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even hopes best forgotten are silenced{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:10.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as corruption spreads out before our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.59,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consign it to darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:17.30,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ego on trial{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:28.48,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a moment of hesitation is seen ecstasy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:33.94,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Fireballman vs. the Devilfiend"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireballman,\NI'm going to get strong like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and be a hero of justice, like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.79,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord6\be6}"Episode 5: 'Banquet of Wishes'"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, this is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you\Nrunning away for?! Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i} be of service to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tabata, the Code: Breakers\Nhave infiltrated the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if they're the devil;\NI won't let them interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to wonder, why are they\Ndoing research on these so-called
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"special abilities" in a government facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since Code: Breakers\Nare a government agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami and I both operate\Nunder orders from the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...? The Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. So even in the\Nform of politicians or policemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,evil can never escape from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably kids\Nwho possess special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gathered here from all over Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and researched in all sorts of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what exactly is\Nthe government trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can say? But they are in\Nprotective care, so no foul, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's those two large men earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why\Ntheir power ran out while fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think they went Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that before,\Ntoo. What is "Lost"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lost is when...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like a hospital in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just like in the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For a hospital, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, Code: Breakers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be Tabata, right?\NCarrying on special ability research?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those muscle-bound idiots were\Nthe results of your research, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still no equal\Nfor a genuine Code: Breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Diet member Tabata Shigeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've at\Nleast heard his name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one in charge of this research.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the government really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The real matter is still to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, the organs are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tabata, Eden is furious\Nabout your unauthorized killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't told to\Ntraffic in their organs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude, referring to us as "such a thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're doing is helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids whose special powers are low
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are useless, and good for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And as such, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Making use of their organs,\Nat least, is for the greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way something like\Nthis can be permitted!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My, such a spirited little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we ought to take her apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...if they're no use, then who needs them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you get it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you of any use to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're of no use, then who needs you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I don't need your organs, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be for the greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He vaporized it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, keep back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, so close! I even turned it to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it, will you!\NWe're not here for you guys anyhow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen this,\Nwe can't let you leave here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your organs are all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing, for a\NCode: Breaker to have to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, that's one pesky ability he's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, there's something weird about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he carrying that\Nheavy-looking thing around on his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Code: Breaker for you, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?\NCome on and turn up the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what becomes of useless children, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A sneak attack?!\NAren't you the coward, Code: Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheap shots, huh? How nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, sure enough, there's some gimmick
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to those things they're carrying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll just destroy it directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised? This is made from carbon fiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't destroy it\Nwith your special ability, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, you really {\i1}are{\i} a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from behind?\NYou really {\i1}are{\i} a nasty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on and make with the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'll do to you what I did to your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't take your eyes off of me!\N- Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Power's used up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are useless, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My word, little kids are hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Their power is all used up so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill... them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They... cut up Brother... my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...because their powers are weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a voice... my little sister's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...saying "Help me"...\NBut then I stopped hearing her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped hearing my sister's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill... them... Get back for my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them... please! Kill the ones who...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...killed my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! How the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye; a tooth for a tooth;
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the hammer of justice for evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! No! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just evil that kills off other evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as though\Nit will take away your grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,nor will the dead be brought back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so... thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lousy hypocrites!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not right for\Nhim to kill any more people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, have you ever wondered\Nwhy heroes are able to be heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Heroes are heroes because\Nthey kill those who are evil
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Sakura, your words won't\Nreach him while you're of two minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not of two minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They cut up Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill... them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything! Not {\i1}you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know my pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, what's the matter?\NWho are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabata's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisa, that young man\Nis a hero of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Mister, are you Fireballman?\NYou really did come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa told me that Fireballman\Nwould come for my sickness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and trade the bad part of\Nmy tummy for something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, Fireballman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm all better, I'm gonna\Nbe a hero like you, Fireballman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, Tabata was doing all this to find
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a suitable donor organ for his own daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You counted yourself lucky to be ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to oversee this special ability research,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,since you could find a\Nmatching organ for your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Mr. Tabata, though what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,may be right before\Nyour eyes, it's still wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisa needs the organ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can she wait year\Nafter year for a donor to show up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd kill other children\Nin your daughter's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How self-serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! You have\Nno right talking to me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're killers, too, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You use your special powers\Nto go on your killing sprees!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Those children\Nare just those who will end up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,going around killing\Npeople as the state's dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, isn't it far better to\Nuse their organs, to save people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with sacrificing\Ndogs so that Chisa can survive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to save Chisa. Chisa is all I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For my daughter's sake, I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it is for your daughter's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't change the\Nfact that you are a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any heart at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, already...\NThat boy had his brother killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and suffered so much,\Nhe wished death on someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you {\i1}were{\i}\Ndoing it for your daughter's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,walking all over others,\Nand sacrificing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just... You can just!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just... You can just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy was warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart was beating, thumpity-thump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But he quickly grew cold,\Nand his heart also went weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is for a life to vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You are warm, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You are warm, just like that boy was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive, and there's no\Nreason why you should be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Ogami, don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a guy like this is alive.\NDon't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the reasons were,\NI should not have killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Fireballman!\NYou have to face the Devilfiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I made lots of people suffer,\Nand killed them! Is that wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- T-Tabata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Papa, what are you...\N- T-Tabata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chisa, I'm sorry.\NI killed for the sake of my own desires,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and turned into a Devilfiend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Fireballman here\Nhas come to put me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die! Fireballman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireballman, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you hurt Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he is a Devilfiend,\Nhe's still my papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Fireballman! Die! Die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you resentful? If you're\Nresentful, then live through this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then come after me to\Nkill me. I'll remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll ever forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She overexerted herself,\Nbeing sick and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact the medical team.\NShe'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami... You said that on\Npurpose, to make her hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think that by hating you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd become her purpose for living?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your methods are problematic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but Ogami, that was the act of a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself evil, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how evil those I face may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,once I kill them,\NI am no longer a hero of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Tabata has been terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all right.\NThe research data is in its usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, who you could be funneling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the special ability children's research data to,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tsuno. The secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A Code: Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like the mastermind\Nis on the other end of that phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to give me your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!\NThere's a Code: Breaker here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for carrying out your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... he set me up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tsuno committed suicide.\NIs this your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toki. It's been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. Code 0 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...you, Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing you, Toki. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister,\Nthe unit has secured the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They are being moved to Laboratory 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, letting Tabata\Nhead up the special ability research
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine, him resorting to what\Nhe did for his daughter's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's utterly unfathomable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with special abilities\Nare not to be used idly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your master also interested
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in those special ability children?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:01.63,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you, too, will know{\i}\N{\i1}where that white crow is heading{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:07.30,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fly through the brilliant city,{\i}\N{\i1}unnoticed by all around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:21.82,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking only for a reason to live{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:27.20,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashamed of our hollow selves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:31.99,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we just laugh and go along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:37.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rules the world has decided on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:42.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped bare, following{\i}\N{\i1}wherever our instincts lead{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:46.42,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the truth from{\i}\N{\i1}which we've averted our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:51.05,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verdicts handed down for no one's sake{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:55.89,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cast off the dark robes and get on your feet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:00.69,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure white wishes become our wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:05.36,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shake off your hesitations now, and fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:13.78,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have no fear; the answers{\i}\N{\i1}lie beyond the darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If something is going\Nto just disappear in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it's better that it\Nnever was from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time,\N"Code: Breaker" episode 6, "Lost One."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is our destiny.
